seeing you here or at the synagogue.

465
00:52:34,752 --> 00:52:38,525
Well actually,
I hail from Alexandria.

466
00:52:38,605 --> 00:52:41,100
You must be here on business?
- Exactly.

467
00:52:41,180 --> 00:52:45,600
What do you do, son?
- I.. My business..

468
00:52:45,820 --> 00:52:48,300
I deal in diamonds and gems.

469
00:52:48,380 --> 00:52:49,780
Fantastic. That is fantastic.

470
00:52:50,260 --> 00:52:54,420
