"I will take a cure
for my heart from him."

581
01:02:23,263 --> 01:02:28,143
"I will take a cure
for my heart from him."

582
01:02:28,423 --> 01:02:33,343
"Neither would I have smiled,
nor would he have come close."

583
01:02:33,423 --> 01:02:38,462
"That's what I have been
punished for, what do I do?"

